      "description": "2020 sedan in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable scratches and minor dents from regular use. Mechanically functional, but has some issues that may need attention in the near term. Interior shows moderate wear. Suitable for a buyer comfortable with a vehicle that needs some upkeep.",
      "price": 20000.0,
